title: According to MSNBC focus group, Hillary is kinda “bitchy” [video] | U. S. Politics
text:
(Before It's News)
CDN – http://www.conservativedailynews.com
Shannon, a member of a New Hampshire MSNBC political focus group, was asked how she felt about Hillary Clinton. Shannon responded that she found the former first lady off-putting “You know, when she’s — I don’t want to use the word,” laughing. Then she whispered “bitchy” to Halperin.
The group as a whole talked about how condescending Hillary is and how it will likely cost her the election.
